name: Aggressive Growth
text:
Search your library for up to two basic land cards, reveal those cards, put one onto the battlefield tapped and the other into your hand, then shuffle.
If {u}{r} was spent to cast this spell, earthshake 2. (Put two +1/+1 counters on target land you control. You may have it become a 0/0 Elemental creature until end of turn. It's still a land.)
